	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107889078291416017">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.utne.com/">Utne.com</a>.&nbsp; This page is cited by Jack Park concerning a paper on on social change and how all social change arises from conversations (my words).&nbsp; I need to get the rest of the citation.&nbsp; Ah, it is Margaret J. Wheatley, "All Social Change beins with a conversation," 2002 July 28.<br>
