	<a href="http://twiki.org/">TWiki - A Web Based Collaboration Platform</a>.&nbsp; I stumble across this Perl-based wiki implementation from time to time.&nbsp; As much as I don't want to struggle with Perl, there is clearly much offered here as a benchmark and best-of-breed.&nbsp; I really am committed to JavaScript, though, and on my hosted sites, ASP as well.&nbsp; Oh well.<br>
